OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome showers
OL,6,Fto start the evening, heavy at times,
OL,7,Fbut these will slowly die out. Further
OL,8,Fshowers will then spread in from the
OL,9,Fwest overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA largely cloudy day with a
OL,12,Ffew showers but becoming drier and
OL,13,Fbrighter during the late afternoon
OL,14,Finto the evening.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,17,FCloudy with outbreaks of rain on
OL,18,FThursday but becoming drier and
OL,19,Fbrighter later. Sunshine and scattered
OL,20,Fshowers on Friday then dry, bright and
OL,21,Fturning warmer on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
